languages.text: "За грехи Кубиса Дельфима пусть отвечает братство, к которому он принадлежал. Адептус Механикус дурно следят за своими членами".
"Let the priesthood to which Cubis Delphim belonged answer for his crimes. The Adeptus Mechanicus would do well to watch their members more closely."

languages.text: “这件事情应该让库比斯·德尔菲姆的修会负责。机械修会应该学会更加密切地监视成员的一言一行。”

traits.locale_text: “这件事情应该让库比斯·德尔菲姆的兄弟会负责。机械修会应该学会更加密切地监视成员的一言一行。”

languages.text: «Que el sacerdocio al que Cubis Delphim pertenecía pague por sus crímenes. El Adeptus Mechanicus debería prestar más atención a sus miembros».
languages.original_text: "Let the priesthood to which Cubis Delphim belonged answer for his crimes. The Adeptus Mechanicus would do well to watch their members more closely."

traits.locale_text: «Que la hermandad a la que Cubis Delphim pertenecía pague por sus crímenes. El Adeptus Mechanicus debería prestar más atención a sus miembros».

languages.text: « Que le clergé de Cubis Delphim réponde de ses crimes. L'Adeptus Mechanicus devrait surveiller ses membres de plus près. »
languages.original_text: "Let the priesthood to which Cubis Delphim belonged answer for his crimes. The Adeptus Mechanicus would do well to watch their members more closely."

traits.locale_text: « Que la confrérie de Cubis Delphim réponde de ses crimes. L'Adeptus Mechanicus devrait surveiller ses membres de plus près. »

languages.text: "Soll doch die Priesterschaft, zu der Cubis Delphim gehörte, für seine Verbrechen einstehen. Das Adeptus Mechanicus wäre gut beraten, seine Mitglieder genauer zu beobachten."
languages.original_text: "Let the priesthood to which Cubis Delphim belonged answer for his crimes. The Adeptus Mechanicus would do well to watch their members more closely."

traits.locale_text: "Soll doch die Bruderschaft, zu der Cubis Delphim gehörte, für seine Verbrechen geradestehen. Das Adeptus Mechanicus wäre gut beraten, seine Mitglieder genauer zu beobachten."

languages.text: "Suçları için Cubis Delphim'in ait olduğu rahiplik sorumlu tutulsun. Adeptus Mechanicus'un, mensuplarını daha dikkatli gözlemlemesi gerekir."
languages.original_text: "Let the priesthood to which Cubis Delphim belonged answer for his crimes. The Adeptus Mechanicus would do well to watch their members more closely."

traits.locale_text: "Suçları için Cubis Delphim'in ait olduğu rahiplik sorumlu tutulsun. Adeptus Mechanicus'un, üyelerini daha dikkatli gözlemlemesi gerekir."
